WEBVTT

00:10.600 --> 00:12.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

01:06.540 --> 01:08.000
[The Eternal Fragrance]

01:08.000 --> 01:11.980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

01:12.020 --> 01:15.140
[Episode 31]

01:17.390 --> 01:18.370
Have you found the compass?

01:25.670 --> 01:26.370
Great.

01:30.000 --> 01:30.650
Promise me.

01:32.960 --> 01:34.250
Take our people back across the sea.

01:36.270 --> 01:37.220
You and Lifei

01:39.240 --> 01:41.370
must live well.

01:43.390 --> 01:43.940
Alright.

02:10.910 --> 02:13.060
Mu has gone with Jiaping.

02:13.800 --> 02:17.340
We don't know how Lifei and the others are doing.

02:21.110 --> 02:21.620
Mr. Zuo,

02:22.800 --> 02:24.130
I'm heading back to Duanming City now.

02:24.520 --> 02:25.810
If the mountain-sea barrier falls,

02:26.150 --> 02:27.570
please look after the disciples

02:27.710 --> 02:28.940
who've retreated inland

02:30.080 --> 02:32.620
and preserve one last hope for the immortal sects.

02:35.990 --> 02:36.570
Don't worry.

02:50.990 --> 02:52.780
The East Sea will witness a tough battle.

02:53.040 --> 02:53.810
We healers

02:54.040 --> 02:55.410
are meant to save lives.

02:55.960 --> 02:57.300
If we don't go to the East Sea now,

02:57.670 --> 02:58.740
then when will we?

02:59.080 --> 02:59.970
Let me pack.

03:00.430 --> 03:01.780
I'll go with you to Duanming City.

03:02.150 --> 03:02.650
Great!

03:02.900 --> 03:03.940
Let's go together!

03:09.590 --> 03:10.180
Take care.

03:10.990 --> 03:11.460
Take care.

03:12.150 --> 03:12.810
Both of you,

03:14.240 --> 03:14.780
take care.

03:18.320 --> 03:20.940
Thanks to Prince Ying

03:20.960 --> 03:21.780
and Immortal Cuixuan's strategy,

03:22.080 --> 03:23.370
we dealt Yecha a heavy blow.

03:23.800 --> 03:24.460
Otherwise,

03:24.870 --> 03:26.130
if the demons had taken the Divine Tree,

03:26.620 --> 03:27.740
it would have been a catastrophe.

03:28.590 --> 03:29.530
What a pity.

03:30.480 --> 03:33.220
Immortal Cuixuan fell into Yecha's hands.

03:33.900 --> 03:35.250
I've buried my master.

03:36.520 --> 03:37.970
He died fighting demons.

03:39.040 --> 03:40.130
He has no regrets.

03:42.590 --> 03:43.020
Everyone,

03:44.550 --> 03:46.410
I will dedicate myself to slaying demons

03:47.110 --> 03:48.300
and upholding my master's will.

03:48.760 --> 03:49.410
But

03:49.590 --> 03:50.340
the Divine Tree has let the Demon Lord

03:50.360 --> 03:51.620
slip away time and again.

03:52.360 --> 03:53.300
She harbors ill intent.

03:53.760 --> 03:55.460
Keeping her around is a liability.

03:56.320 --> 03:56.970
I say

03:57.550 --> 03:58.940
the Divine Tree must be eliminated.

04:01.150 --> 04:02.900
Lifei must have been bewitched

04:02.920 --> 04:03.690
by the Demon Lord.

04:04.150 --> 04:04.940
I trust her.

04:05.240 --> 04:06.970
This isn't about trust.

04:07.670 --> 04:10.410
Duanming City can't afford another disaster.

04:10.870 --> 04:11.300
Exactly.

04:12.270 --> 04:13.130
The Sea Calamity is coming.

04:13.360 --> 04:14.180
The demons covet her.

04:14.430 --> 04:15.650
If they come for her again...

04:15.670 --> 04:17.090
Lifei is my future wife.

04:17.870 --> 04:19.250
I'll keep a close watch on her.

04:21.120 --> 04:23.210
She won't fall into demon hands again.

04:46.680 --> 04:47.210
My Lord,

04:47.680 --> 04:49.330
Jiang Lifei is under house arrest by Ji Tongzhou.

04:49.710 --> 04:50.570
She's safe for now.

04:55.560 --> 04:56.620
This ancient text says

04:57.710 --> 04:58.890
that when the Sea Calamity comes,

04:59.440 --> 05:00.810
the seawater will surge backward into Guixu,

05:01.440 --> 05:02.540
breaching the heavenly chasm.

05:03.030 --> 05:06.570
With this Xuantian Biluo Compass,

05:07.080 --> 05:09.740
we can find a way across the sea

05:10.760 --> 05:11.890
and cross Guixu.

05:13.390 --> 05:14.500
Cross Guixu?

05:15.520 --> 05:16.860
Legend says Guixu can devour the heavens

05:16.880 --> 05:17.660
and has countless dark spirits.

05:18.000 --> 05:18.980
How can anyone cross it?

05:19.790 --> 05:20.740
There's always a way.

05:26.640 --> 05:27.250
My Lord,

05:28.030 --> 05:29.010
aren't you going to save Jiang Lifei?

05:32.000 --> 05:33.420
I have my own duty to fulfill,

05:33.760 --> 05:34.980
and you do what you must.

05:38.230 --> 05:38.740
No need.

05:46.320 --> 05:49.940
We each have our own duties to fulfill.

06:05.710 --> 06:07.330
I had these pastries specially made.

06:12.200 --> 06:13.060
All your favorites.

06:14.320 --> 06:15.570
Why did you side with Cuixuan?

06:26.710 --> 06:27.570
The immortal sects are in decline.

06:28.150 --> 06:29.100
He's a senior master.

06:29.680 --> 06:30.940
And he's willing to help me fight the demons.

06:32.560 --> 06:33.540
Why shouldn't I work with him?

06:34.230 --> 06:35.210
He killed my master

06:35.230 --> 06:36.210
and Mr. Shen!

06:37.200 --> 06:38.180
He's monstrous.

06:38.200 --> 06:39.770
You won't end well working with him!

06:44.320 --> 06:46.250
Does doing everything for the greater good ever end well?

06:49.200 --> 06:49.860
My uncle,

06:50.440 --> 06:50.940
my brother,

06:51.560 --> 06:52.620
and your senior brothers and sisters.

06:53.520 --> 06:54.420
Did any of them get a good ending?

06:57.320 --> 06:58.300
If they knew

06:59.390 --> 07:00.210
this is what

07:00.590 --> 07:01.940
their sacrifice bought,

07:03.320 --> 07:04.420
do you think they'd rest

07:04.440 --> 07:05.180
in peace?

07:07.030 --> 07:08.180
They didn't do it

07:09.230 --> 07:10.740
for their own good endings.

07:11.470 --> 07:12.300
They did it for you,

07:12.880 --> 07:13.620
for me,

07:14.790 --> 07:16.690
and for everyone they died protecting.

07:18.640 --> 07:19.180
Tongzhou.

07:19.910 --> 07:20.810
Wrong is wrong.

07:21.440 --> 07:22.770
Nothing justifies it.

07:23.680 --> 07:24.980
Cuixuan offered himself to the demons

07:25.000 --> 07:26.130
for his ambition.

07:26.710 --> 07:27.300
And you?

07:28.640 --> 07:29.690
What were you fighting for

07:30.320 --> 07:31.250
all this way?

07:32.230 --> 07:33.130
Did you forget?

07:47.120 --> 07:47.890
What did I do wrong?

07:50.440 --> 07:51.130
I fight demons

07:51.150 --> 07:51.980
and protect the immortal sects.

07:52.560 --> 07:53.330
What did I do wrong?

07:54.390 --> 07:55.570
You're the one who's wrong!

07:56.830 --> 07:58.210
You chose to betray me

07:58.520 --> 07:59.570
and be with Lei Xiuyuan.

08:00.200 --> 08:01.300
The Divine Tree and Yecha.

08:02.080 --> 08:03.180
A thousand years

08:03.200 --> 08:04.370
haven't changed a thing!

08:07.200 --> 08:08.010
What do you mean?

08:12.150 --> 08:13.330
This is my ancestor.

08:14.120 --> 08:15.370
I only recently found out

08:15.680 --> 08:16.570
that this scroll

08:16.760 --> 08:18.010
records my ancestor's past.

08:18.760 --> 08:19.250
Turns out

08:19.880 --> 08:21.010
he loved the Divine Tree as well.

08:22.030 --> 08:23.370
But the Divine Tree abandoned him

08:23.710 --> 08:25.180
and fled with Yecha.

08:26.560 --> 08:28.060
With the Divine Tree's power, Yecha

08:28.640 --> 08:29.500
unleashed the Sea Calamity

08:29.520 --> 08:30.330
and overturned the Central Plains.

08:33.270 --> 08:34.810
My ancestor trained in Xuanhua Sacred Fire

08:35.120 --> 08:36.330
to protect the people.

08:37.230 --> 08:38.850
He led the immortal sects to quell the Sea Calamity.

08:39.400 --> 08:40.780
But his spirit power was depleted,

08:41.920 --> 08:42.570
and he died soon after.

08:44.200 --> 08:44.730
Lifei,

08:46.160 --> 08:47.610
are you really going to make the same mistake?

08:56.200 --> 08:57.420
That thousand-year-old record

08:57.750 --> 08:58.540
may not be true.

08:59.870 --> 09:00.570
I am me.

09:01.160 --> 09:01.970
The Divine Tree is the Divine Tree.

09:02.830 --> 09:04.210
I won't repeat the past.

09:04.750 --> 09:05.330
Besides,

09:06.160 --> 09:07.660
Xiuyuan isn't the Yecha from back then.

09:08.200 --> 09:10.020
He truly wants to help us withstand the Sea Calamity.

09:10.630 --> 09:11.940
Why are you still defending him?

09:20.660 --> 09:21.260
Lifei,

09:21.870 --> 09:23.380
do you really need to see bloodshed again

09:24.320 --> 09:25.570
to realize you're wrong?

09:25.750 --> 09:26.780
You're the one who's wrong!

09:27.960 --> 09:29.020
The Sea Calamity is coming.

09:29.830 --> 09:31.330
Our enemy isn't the demons!

09:32.320 --> 09:33.540
We need to fight the Sea Calamity.

09:33.660 --> 09:34.940
Trust Xiuyuan.

09:35.510 --> 09:36.260
Trust me.

09:43.440 --> 09:44.490
Whether I trust you or not doesn't matter.

09:45.280 --> 09:45.970
In this life,

09:46.510 --> 09:47.850
I won't let Yecha take you away.

09:53.710 --> 09:54.330
Forget it.

09:55.510 --> 09:56.490
Nothing I say matters.

10:05.990 --> 10:06.940
Take your jade pendant back!

10:12.830 --> 10:13.900
I never take back

10:14.710 --> 10:15.730
what I give.

10:21.940 --> 10:22.420
Here.

10:22.830 --> 10:23.540
Eat something.

10:25.820 --> 10:26.300
Eat!

10:38.420 --> 10:39.570
Xingzheng Hall's restriction spell?

11:02.420 --> 11:02.970
Changyue.

11:03.560 --> 11:04.060
Gelin.

11:04.590 --> 11:06.610
We heard about you and Lifei's engagement

11:07.350 --> 11:08.300
and rushed over overnight.

11:08.870 --> 11:10.610
Didn't expect so much to have happened.

11:10.990 --> 11:12.330
A lot has happened indeed.

11:12.870 --> 11:13.970
You rushed over overnight.

11:14.180 --> 11:15.300
Why not settle in first?

11:15.420 --> 11:16.300
We can talk another day.

11:16.590 --> 11:17.210
Tongzhou,

11:17.820 --> 11:20.660
I heard Lifei's been locked in her room for days.

11:21.230 --> 11:22.020
How is she?

11:22.460 --> 11:23.210
We want to see her.

11:25.560 --> 11:26.540
She's my future wife.

11:26.940 --> 11:27.810
Of course she's fine.

11:28.350 --> 11:29.660
Then why are you keeping her in there

11:29.680 --> 11:30.690
with a restriction spell?

11:33.340 --> 11:34.970
Right now, both immortals and demons

11:35.470 --> 11:36.810
are after Lifei's power.

11:38.060 --> 11:39.570
And she was wounded by Lei Xiuyuan.

11:40.220 --> 11:40.900
She's weak.

11:41.560 --> 11:42.260
Hard times

11:42.510 --> 11:43.850
call for hard measures.

11:44.110 --> 11:45.420
Wounded by Xiuyuan?

11:49.940 --> 11:51.180
Lei Xiuyuan has fully fallen to the demon side.

11:51.680 --> 11:53.020
He killed Mr. Shen,

11:53.510 --> 11:54.810
and when he couldn't take the Divine Tree,

11:55.560 --> 11:56.810
he struck Lifei.

11:57.560 --> 11:58.730
But we're not outsiders.

11:58.750 --> 11:59.730
Surely we can see Lifei.

12:05.470 --> 12:06.330
She just rested.

12:06.980 --> 12:07.690
Come back tomorrow

12:08.180 --> 12:08.810
after she wakes.

12:09.350 --> 12:09.810
Then we...

12:13.340 --> 12:13.780
Alright.

12:14.420 --> 12:15.300
We'll come tomorrow.

12:23.180 --> 12:24.850
What's Ji Tongzhou doing?

12:26.830 --> 12:28.730
I wonder how Lifei really is.

12:36.040 --> 12:37.730
I listened carefully to Lifei's heartbeat.

12:38.280 --> 12:39.020
She's not in danger.

12:39.630 --> 12:41.940
Guess Tongzhou hasn't been too harsh on her.

12:42.830 --> 12:44.180
We've known each other since we were young

12:44.920 --> 12:45.900
and share deep bonds.

12:46.750 --> 12:48.970
I trust Tongzhou will protect Lifei.

12:49.440 --> 12:50.140
Forget it.

12:50.660 --> 12:52.420
I actually wished them well.

12:52.830 --> 12:54.540
I never thought he'd collude with that snake Cuixuan

12:54.540 --> 12:55.210
and deceive Lifei.

12:56.320 --> 12:58.450
Cuixuan nearly devoured Lifei before.

13:00.040 --> 13:00.570
Alright.

13:01.470 --> 13:04.780
Duanming City's situation is complicated right now.

13:05.200 --> 13:07.060
Tongzhou has to stay fair

13:07.510 --> 13:08.380
and protect Lifei.

13:09.440 --> 13:11.330
That's no easy task for him.

13:11.750 --> 13:14.090
Right now, the most important thing is the Sea Calamity.

13:15.280 --> 13:15.810
Exactly.

13:17.350 --> 13:18.690
On this trip to Simo's hometown,

13:19.110 --> 13:21.300
we saw that even ordinary people

13:21.320 --> 13:22.260
were in panic

13:22.800 --> 13:23.450
over the Sea Calamity.

13:24.580 --> 13:25.450
As cultivators,

13:26.110 --> 13:27.610
we should protect the people

13:27.960 --> 13:28.810
in times of crisis.

13:29.660 --> 13:30.540
During this Sea Calamity,

13:32.630 --> 13:34.020
we can't afford even a single mistake.

13:35.320 --> 13:37.020
Lu is guarding the mountain-sea barrier.

13:37.280 --> 13:38.180
If anything unusual happens,

13:38.200 --> 13:39.330
he'll send word soon.

13:41.040 --> 13:41.610
Gelin.

13:44.110 --> 13:45.380
I think

13:45.750 --> 13:47.970
Lu is a reliable man.

13:48.870 --> 13:50.090
I can rest easy

13:50.350 --> 13:51.900
entrusting you to him.

13:52.080 --> 13:52.780
Changyue.

13:53.440 --> 13:54.060
Alright.

13:54.440 --> 13:55.300
I'll go check on Tongzhou,

13:55.750 --> 13:57.140
so that he won't overthink.

13:57.800 --> 13:58.420
Wait.

13:59.040 --> 13:59.970
I'll come with you.

14:00.830 --> 14:01.300
Alright.

14:01.660 --> 14:02.380
I'm leaving.

14:31.800 --> 14:33.140
Gelin and Changyue came to see you,

14:34.040 --> 14:34.900
but I sent them away.

14:35.830 --> 14:37.210
How long are you planning to keep me locked up?

14:38.990 --> 14:39.660
You want to leave?

14:42.200 --> 14:43.610
I have important things to do.

14:44.710 --> 14:45.810
If you're not going to kill me,

14:46.320 --> 14:47.300
then let me go.

14:47.990 --> 14:49.140
Ji Tongzhou, wake up.

14:50.560 --> 14:51.730
Xiuyuan needs us.

14:55.280 --> 14:56.380
Needs us?

14:57.080 --> 14:58.090
You're going to Lei Xiuyuan?

15:01.040 --> 15:02.300
Don't be so stubborn.

15:04.280 --> 15:05.570
I'm stubborn?

15:06.080 --> 15:07.300
What are you really trying to do?

15:09.440 --> 15:10.540
The Sea Calamity is coming.

15:10.920 --> 15:11.780
There's not much time.

15:12.320 --> 15:13.090
Let me out.

15:13.750 --> 15:15.260
Maybe I can stop it.

15:15.510 --> 15:16.300
Stop it?

15:17.280 --> 15:18.420
How?

15:19.510 --> 15:20.180
Lifei,

15:20.960 --> 15:22.380
you used to be better

15:22.400 --> 15:23.610
at lying than this.

15:24.040 --> 15:24.610
Tongzhou,

15:25.710 --> 15:26.780
the three of us have been through

15:26.800 --> 15:28.140
life and death together for years.

15:28.510 --> 15:29.450
Trust me this once!

15:30.750 --> 15:31.940
Even if I trust you,

15:32.350 --> 15:33.060
what about everyone else?

15:34.040 --> 15:34.900
To them,

15:34.920 --> 15:35.970
you're just the Fruit of the Divine Tree.

15:36.080 --> 15:36.970
An anomaly!

15:37.800 --> 15:39.420
Only I see you as human.

15:40.320 --> 15:41.850
I've given you my all,

15:42.080 --> 15:43.330
yet you just want to leave!

15:44.320 --> 15:45.210
You see me as human?

15:47.040 --> 15:48.210
Then why lock me up?

15:48.510 --> 15:49.850
I'm protecting you!

15:50.160 --> 15:50.970
Every immortal sect

15:50.990 --> 15:52.210
is after your spirit power.

15:52.230 --> 15:53.660
Only I can protect you!

15:57.960 --> 15:59.260
Don't you want my spirit power?

16:02.440 --> 16:04.450
You still need a lot to break through

16:05.320 --> 16:06.940
the fifth level of Xuanhua Sacred Fire, don't you?

16:10.200 --> 16:13.810
Sometimes I wish I could live in ignorance.

16:15.870 --> 16:17.260
Because being clear-headed

16:18.710 --> 16:19.940
hurts too much.

16:31.280 --> 16:32.060
What do you know?

16:35.630 --> 16:36.810
I wish I knew nothing.

16:39.750 --> 16:40.490
Yes.

16:41.230 --> 16:42.420
I do want your spirit power.

16:42.990 --> 16:44.780
Once I break through the fifth level,

16:45.040 --> 16:46.330
I'll be unstoppable!

16:46.870 --> 16:47.540
And then no one

16:47.560 --> 16:48.850
will ever take you from me again!

16:52.160 --> 16:54.060
If you wanted spirit power, you could've just asked me.

16:55.080 --> 16:56.140
I would've given it to you.

16:58.560 --> 16:59.900
But you kept hiding

17:00.440 --> 17:01.450
and scheming.

17:02.870 --> 17:03.900
Because you know what you did

17:03.920 --> 17:04.970
was wrong yourself.

17:06.080 --> 17:07.610
You just can't control it, can you?

17:07.960 --> 17:08.340
You!

17:12.230 --> 17:12.940
Fine.

17:13.510 --> 17:14.730
Then I'll just take it from you!

17:15.230 --> 17:16.210
Tongzhou, I'm sorry.

17:18.230 --> 17:19.290
I was wrong.

17:21.070 --> 17:22.530
I thought the bond between the three of us

17:23.400 --> 17:24.900
was enough to see us through any crisis

17:26.270 --> 17:28.050
and help you let go of your obsession.

17:30.200 --> 17:31.340
But I found out

17:33.120 --> 17:35.050
it only fed your darker side.

17:39.960 --> 17:41.050
We hurt you.

17:42.840 --> 17:44.380
So whatever you do,

17:46.710 --> 17:47.730
I won't blame you.

17:50.470 --> 17:51.450
Jiang Lifei!

18:03.550 --> 18:04.420
Your Highness,

18:05.120 --> 18:06.580
since you can't do it,

18:06.880 --> 18:09.450
how about I step in?

18:18.680 --> 18:19.690
Your cultivation

18:20.120 --> 18:21.380
has grown fast in just a few days.

18:27.160 --> 18:29.210
You collected Cuixuan's body.

18:30.120 --> 18:31.250
Could it be that you...?

18:37.200 --> 18:39.660
He had demonic energy and spirit power.

18:40.470 --> 18:41.970
It'd be a waste

18:42.360 --> 18:43.690
to let it rot.

18:47.920 --> 18:49.250
You devoured your own master.

18:50.200 --> 18:51.580
You're insane.

18:52.310 --> 18:53.730
It seems both the immortal sects

18:54.680 --> 18:56.010
and demon clans have their share of scum!

18:58.680 --> 19:01.900
Jiang Lifei, no matter how sharp your tongue,

19:02.270 --> 19:05.250
no one's coming to save you this time.

19:16.440 --> 19:17.180
It was you.

19:18.990 --> 19:20.690
You killed Zhaomin!

19:34.070 --> 19:35.210
You animal!

19:36.160 --> 19:36.940
Why?

19:44.960 --> 19:45.860
Why?

19:46.470 --> 19:47.420
If I hadn't killed her,

19:48.200 --> 19:49.580
would you have given up on Yecha?

19:50.880 --> 19:52.420
Would you have killed him yourself?

19:56.920 --> 19:58.050
What a pity.

19:58.710 --> 20:00.860
You two still have feelings for each other.

20:03.880 --> 20:05.730
Truly, those not of our kind

20:06.680 --> 20:07.900
must be wiped out!

20:17.550 --> 20:18.140
Lifei.

20:28.550 --> 20:31.290
The Divine Tree's power is truly remarkable.

20:32.270 --> 20:33.140
Your Highness,

20:34.270 --> 20:36.140
join me now.

20:36.710 --> 20:39.900
Together we'll rule the world.

20:43.880 --> 20:44.770
Fine.

21:14.880 --> 21:15.450
This is...?

21:22.990 --> 21:23.770
Your Highness.

21:33.360 --> 21:34.770
Dragon-Phoenix Sanctuary Pendant.

21:36.230 --> 21:37.820
Dragon and Phoenix, bound as one.

21:39.120 --> 21:40.380
If you absorb the Phoenix,

21:42.030 --> 21:44.010
the Dragon will turn on you.

21:46.120 --> 21:47.050
You're right.

21:48.200 --> 21:49.580
You have demonic energy and spirit power.

21:49.600 --> 21:50.900
It'd be a waste

21:52.550 --> 21:54.180
to let it rot.

21:57.230 --> 21:58.970
I worked so hard for this...

21:59.840 --> 22:01.730
I won't accept it!

22:06.680 --> 22:08.290
You should be honored to help me

22:09.270 --> 22:10.580
achieve the Great Dao!

22:20.920 --> 22:21.730
Stop!

22:27.750 --> 22:29.140
If you don't stop, you'll fall to the demon!

22:30.400 --> 22:31.290
Stop!

22:31.310 --> 22:32.340
Tongzhou!

22:42.510 --> 22:44.450
You're crazy!

22:57.070 --> 22:57.940
I'm crazy?

23:00.510 --> 23:01.970
You drove me crazy!

23:03.360 --> 23:04.730
I did so much for you.

23:05.440 --> 23:06.860
Why do you treat me like this?

23:06.960 --> 23:07.970
Why?

23:13.360 --> 23:16.690
Tongzhou, let it go.

23:17.680 --> 23:18.380
Let it go?

23:21.710 --> 23:23.450
You all betrayed me.

23:24.200 --> 23:25.820
Why should I let any of you go?

23:26.840 --> 23:27.860
Why?

23:37.750 --> 23:38.450
Your Highness!

23:39.160 --> 23:39.940
What are you doing?

23:54.470 --> 23:55.250
What am I doing?

23:58.470 --> 23:58.940
I...

24:01.360 --> 24:01.770
I was...

24:01.990 --> 24:02.420
Your Highness.

24:02.750 --> 24:03.380
Get away!

24:10.160 --> 24:10.690
Your Highness!

24:34.400 --> 24:36.290
I've mastered the fifth level

24:37.360 --> 24:38.490
of Xuanhua Sacred Fire!

24:41.440 --> 24:43.770
You just can't control it, can you?

24:51.640 --> 24:52.180
No.

24:53.400 --> 24:54.100
I'm not crazy.

24:56.400 --> 24:57.970
I just wanted to become stronger.

24:58.680 --> 24:59.490
What's wrong with that?

25:00.550 --> 25:01.420
What's wrong?

25:07.990 --> 25:08.940
Congratulations,

25:08.960 --> 25:10.290
Your Highness.

25:10.790 --> 25:12.900
Once you've fully absorbed the Divine Tree's power,

25:13.160 --> 25:14.340
your cultivation will reach its peak.

25:14.680 --> 25:17.730
Don't forget to look out for me when that happens.

25:22.920 --> 25:24.380
Who do you think you are?

25:30.680 --> 25:31.420
Your Highness,

25:32.120 --> 25:33.940
why pretend to be so noble?

25:34.200 --> 25:37.140
You're just like us.

25:43.230 --> 25:44.250
I am

25:45.790 --> 25:46.820
not like you.

25:47.270 --> 25:48.180
Yes, you are.

25:50.640 --> 25:52.380
I just saw you absorbing...

26:20.710 --> 26:21.420
Tongzhou.

26:22.070 --> 26:22.450
What...

26:25.200 --> 26:26.140
What were you doing?

26:29.640 --> 26:30.340
Are you crazy?

26:31.270 --> 26:32.530
You're even draining Lifei?

26:34.440 --> 26:34.970
I'm not crazy.

26:36.640 --> 26:37.180
I'm not crazy!

26:39.270 --> 26:39.820
Tongzhou,

26:40.840 --> 26:41.340
don't you remember?

26:42.310 --> 26:43.380
We promised

26:43.840 --> 26:45.140
- Yeah. - to go through life and death together.

26:46.710 --> 26:48.210
Stop now, Tongzhou!

26:49.070 --> 26:50.010
Yes, Tongzhou.

26:50.440 --> 26:51.420
Xiuyuan is the Demon Lord.

26:51.880 --> 26:53.050
Maybe that's not a bad thing.

26:53.990 --> 26:55.860
Perhaps it could change the relationship

26:56.510 --> 26:57.730
between the two clans.

26:59.030 --> 27:00.250
Xiuyuan again.

27:01.200 --> 27:02.340
Always Xiuyuan!

27:03.920 --> 27:04.940
Tongzhou, stop!

27:04.960 --> 27:06.380
- Tongzhou. - Snap out of it!

27:06.640 --> 27:07.970
- Tongzhou. - Wake up, Tongzhou!

27:08.400 --> 27:08.900
Tongzhou!

27:09.120 --> 27:09.490
Tongzhou.

27:09.510 --> 27:10.420
Don't you trust Xiuyuan?

27:10.440 --> 27:10.820
Tongzhou.

27:10.840 --> 27:12.250
Xiuyuan is one of us!

27:14.600 --> 27:15.050
Tongzhou?

27:15.360 --> 27:15.820
Ye.

27:16.160 --> 27:16.900
Tongzhou, what's wrong with you?

27:17.230 --> 27:17.940
Something's off with him.

27:18.200 --> 27:18.690
Go!

27:18.710 --> 27:19.820
Tongzhou, wake up!

27:19.840 --> 27:20.580
Come on, Ye!

27:22.990 --> 27:23.660
Go!

27:24.310 --> 27:24.970
Tongzhou!

27:24.990 --> 27:26.420
Destroy it all!

27:51.310 --> 27:51.900
Tongzhou!

27:52.310 --> 27:53.010
Tongzhou!

27:54.640 --> 27:55.770
Tongzhou, no!

28:47.630 --> 28:50.030
♪The warmth within my arms♪

28:50.030 --> 28:50.580
Tongzhou.

28:51.230 --> 28:52.380
Just an illusion.

28:53.030 --> 28:53.820
None of it was real.

28:55.040 --> 28:57.640
♪In the cold night, how can I♪

28:57.640 --> 28:58.290
All fake.

28:59.920 --> 29:00.660
It must be a dream.

29:00.660 --> 29:02.070
♪Keep you warm until sunrise?♪

29:02.920 --> 29:03.580
None of it was real.

29:03.580 --> 29:04.880
♪My heartbeat freezes♪

29:04.880 --> 29:05.770
It must be fake.

29:05.960 --> 29:09.160
♪I can no longer tell you♪

29:09.560 --> 29:12.760
♪Looking you in the eyes, I cannot♪

29:13.040 --> 29:16.080
♪Utter that line♪

29:16.440 --> 29:18.160
♪Knowing love and hate♪

29:18.480 --> 29:22.400
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

29:24.710 --> 29:25.660
Don't pour anymore.

29:25.790 --> 29:26.940
Alright, Gelin.

29:27.310 --> 29:29.450
We'll never be apart!

29:30.360 --> 29:34.720
♪Last night's stars cast faint glimmers♪

29:35.000 --> 29:37.960
♪But we thought nothing of it♪

29:38.280 --> 29:39.990
♪With a heartbroken cry♪

29:39.990 --> 29:42.620
In three years, the once-in-five-centuries Sea Calamity will come.

29:43.230 --> 29:45.340
We'll gather again at Lugong Town

29:45.680 --> 29:46.450
to stand against it together.

29:47.200 --> 29:48.420
That would make our bond worthwhile.

29:48.440 --> 29:49.050
Well said.

29:49.050 --> 29:51.480
♪Black and gray are all illusions♪

29:52.840 --> 29:54.480
♪You're still screaming♪

29:54.760 --> 29:57.840
♪Running relentlessly without regret♪

29:57.840 --> 29:58.250
No.

29:59.550 --> 30:00.290
No! Ye Ye.

30:00.290 --> 30:02.550
♪The storm looms, yet the wind stands in its way♪

30:02.550 --> 30:03.340
I... I didn't kill you.

30:04.550 --> 30:05.290
I didn't kill you!

30:05.290 --> 30:06.960
♪A final farewell left on the cliff♪

30:07.270 --> 30:11.230
♪Leaping straight into that heartbreaking past♪

30:11.230 --> 30:11.770
I'm sorry.

30:12.600 --> 30:13.250
Sorry.

30:14.790 --> 30:15.450
I'm sorry.

30:15.480 --> 30:18.120
♪Just to keep you safe♪

30:29.610 --> 30:31.120
♪My breath is about to stop♪

30:31.120 --> 30:33.050
I'm so sorry.

30:33.340 --> 30:36.560
♪Those hands can no longer hold yours♪

30:36.700 --> 30:39.900
♪Quietly, I turn into a sky lantern♪

30:40.180 --> 30:43.220
♪To light your way through the night♪

30:43.840 --> 30:44.380
Your Highness.

30:45.120 --> 30:45.690
Stop.

30:46.030 --> 30:46.660
Stop thinking about it.

30:46.920 --> 30:47.620
Please.

30:49.070 --> 30:49.530
I didn't kill you.

30:49.550 --> 30:51.180
Your Highness, stop thinking about it!

30:51.200 --> 30:52.010
Stop!

30:52.470 --> 30:53.290
Your Highness!

30:53.290 --> 30:57.100
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

30:57.480 --> 31:01.810
♪The storm looms, yet the wind stands in its way♪

31:02.170 --> 31:05.010
♪A final farewell left on the cliff♪

31:05.330 --> 31:07.490
♪I'd shatter my soul♪

31:07.890 --> 31:12.400
♪To lay all your days in peace♪

31:12.400 --> 31:13.050
Lifei?

31:13.050 --> 31:14.450
♪Who says that love and hate♪

31:14.600 --> 31:16.050
Lifei, I didn't kill them.

31:16.470 --> 31:17.050
Believe me.

31:17.360 --> 31:18.580
Lifei, I didn't kill Ye Ye.

31:19.550 --> 31:20.180
I was wrong.

31:20.470 --> 31:21.010
I'm sorry.

31:21.160 --> 31:21.690
Forgive me.

31:21.710 --> 31:22.380
- Forgive me. - I know.

31:22.640 --> 31:23.290
I know.

31:23.400 --> 31:24.210
It's not your fault.

31:24.510 --> 31:25.050
Get up.

31:25.640 --> 31:26.970
No! No.

31:27.640 --> 31:28.420
Don't leave me.

31:28.420 --> 31:30.970
♪The storm looms, yet I stand in its way♪

31:31.510 --> 31:32.730
No, Lifei.

31:32.960 --> 31:34.140
Don't leave me.

31:34.530 --> 31:39.400
♪With the light from my fingertips♪

31:39.400 --> 31:40.660
I won't leave you.

31:41.330 --> 31:44.890
♪To wander with you♪

31:46.030 --> 31:46.770
Lifei.

31:47.750 --> 31:48.900
Lifei.

31:51.120 --> 31:51.770
Lu!

31:52.070 --> 31:52.530
Gelin.

31:52.920 --> 31:54.100
Changyue and Ye are gone.

31:54.470 --> 31:55.420
I looked for them all night,

31:55.440 --> 31:56.380
but they're nowhere.

31:57.070 --> 31:58.690
They didn't come back to their room last night.

31:58.960 --> 32:00.250
Last night, strange phenomena occurred in the East Sea.

32:00.510 --> 32:01.450
Dark clouds filled the sky.

32:01.750 --> 32:03.770
I rushed back to Duanming City to reinforce the defensive formation.

32:04.120 --> 32:05.290
All the immortal sects sent people

32:05.440 --> 32:06.250
to patrol the coast,

32:06.470 --> 32:07.380
including Dizang Sect.

32:07.960 --> 32:10.140
Maybe Ye Ye and Changyue went to help.

32:15.510 --> 32:16.250
- What's wrong? - What's happening?

32:21.270 --> 32:22.290
The city wall is collapsing, Lu.

32:29.160 --> 32:29.770
- Mr. Mo? - Mr. Mo?

32:30.310 --> 32:32.420
The Sea Calamity is coming! Go guard the mountain-sea barrier!

32:56.400 --> 32:57.210
You're trying to escape?

32:57.960 --> 32:58.530
There's no time!

32:58.990 --> 32:59.900
Let me out!

33:00.600 --> 33:02.490
Jiang Lifei, you still don't understand me?

33:03.270 --> 33:04.380
After all I've done for you,

33:04.920 --> 33:06.140
you still want to go to Lei Xiuyuan?

33:23.840 --> 33:25.580
Zhurong Fire severs the meridians and the veins.

33:26.120 --> 33:27.530
Your limbs are crippled now.

33:27.960 --> 33:28.770
How can you leave?

33:29.360 --> 33:30.050
There's no time.

33:31.550 --> 33:32.140
Tongzhou.

33:33.510 --> 33:34.660
You'll regret this!

33:35.550 --> 33:37.140
Just stay put.

33:37.790 --> 33:38.530
Don't go anywhere.

33:39.840 --> 33:40.450
Tongzhou!

34:57.550 --> 34:59.010
So the way back across the sea

34:59.670 --> 35:00.530
lies within Guixu.

35:19.960 --> 35:20.610
What is it?

35:29.110 --> 35:30.450
Guixu can devour the heavens

35:31.240 --> 35:32.130
and has countless dark spirits.

35:39.960 --> 35:40.570
Dark spirits?

36:01.990 --> 36:02.530
Mr. Mo,

36:02.990 --> 36:03.940
what will the Sea Calamity be like?

36:04.800 --> 36:05.570
First tsunamis,

36:06.760 --> 36:07.860
then thunder and fire,

36:09.670 --> 36:10.170
then

36:11.800 --> 36:12.420
the end of the world.

36:25.550 --> 36:26.380
Hold on, everyone!

36:36.320 --> 36:37.530
Coward.

36:39.470 --> 36:40.650
Why didn't Changyue and Ye come?

37:11.150 --> 37:11.900
Tongzhou?

37:12.880 --> 37:14.490
Where did he get such boundless spirit power?

37:15.670 --> 37:16.570
It's Prince Ying!

37:16.880 --> 37:17.820
Help now!

37:24.360 --> 37:25.900
Ji Tongzhou must have taken the Divine Tree's power

37:26.280 --> 37:27.570
to become so strong.

37:40.030 --> 37:40.530
What are you doing?

37:50.240 --> 37:51.010
Sect Leader Miao.

37:52.920 --> 37:54.260
Instead of holding back the Sea Calamity,

37:55.030 --> 37:56.650
you're here to devour my spirit power?

37:57.760 --> 37:59.130
Once I absorb the Divine Tree's power,

37:59.510 --> 38:00.570
I'll hold back the Sea Calamity.

38:00.960 --> 38:03.010
Consider it a sacrifice for the world!

38:13.720 --> 38:14.260
Mr. Zhu?

38:17.400 --> 38:18.260
And me!

38:20.280 --> 38:20.970
Sect Leader Miao,

38:21.360 --> 38:22.380
with the calamity upon us,

38:22.670 --> 38:25.940
Dizang Sect abandons the battlefield to take advantage.

38:26.320 --> 38:27.090
Word of this

38:27.470 --> 38:29.900
will disgrace your sect.

38:30.440 --> 38:32.900
I was afraid the demons might attack.

38:33.510 --> 38:34.220
So I came to check.

38:34.880 --> 38:35.780
Since you two are here,

38:36.320 --> 38:38.170
I'll go help defend the barrier.

39:44.110 --> 39:44.650
My Lord.

39:51.070 --> 39:52.530
My Lord, we'll help you.

40:07.440 --> 40:07.970
Rakshasa!

40:09.150 --> 40:09.570
Qiongqi!

40:55.840 --> 40:56.740
Look. Look over there.

40:57.440 --> 40:58.570
Home!

40:58.960 --> 41:00.380
Yes.

41:00.400 --> 41:01.260
- My Lord. - We can go back!

41:01.280 --> 41:02.300
We can go home!

41:02.760 --> 41:03.610
Finally going home!

41:03.630 --> 41:04.820
We can finally go back!

41:05.920 --> 41:06.900
Going home!

41:07.880 --> 41:08.740
Wonderful!

41:10.670 --> 41:11.420
Take our people

41:13.150 --> 41:13.780
home!

41:14.960 --> 41:17.610
Thank you, My Lord!

41:39.240 --> 41:40.530
Take a rest. Let me take over.

41:42.360 --> 41:42.740
Here.

41:53.440 --> 41:54.010
Sir.

42:03.630 --> 42:05.650
How is Miss Jiang?

42:07.550 --> 42:09.530
She was wounded by the fire blade of Zhurong Stone.

42:10.070 --> 42:11.220
Her meridians are destroyed.

42:11.760 --> 42:13.740
A massive infusion of spirit energy

42:14.470 --> 42:17.340
might be her only chance.

42:30.110 --> 42:31.010
Come check Lifei out.

42:42.050 --> 42:42.780
[The Eternal Fragrance]

42:42.780 --> 42:44.560
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

42:55.800 --> 42:59.480
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

42:59.800 --> 43:02.480
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

43:02.560 --> 43:05.800
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

43:05.800 --> 43:09.080
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

43:09.200 --> 43:13.080
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

43:13.360 --> 43:16.560
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

43:16.720 --> 43:22.800
♪No calamity can rival the lingering thread of a fragrance♪

43:23.080 --> 43:27.200
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

43:27.480 --> 43:30.160
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

43:30.360 --> 43:32.280
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

43:32.400 --> 43:36.720
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

43:36.880 --> 43:40.720
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

43:41.080 --> 43:44.080
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

43:44.160 --> 43:50.280
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

43:50.480 --> 43:54.200
♪With you, we melt into mist and haze♪

44:07.440 --> 44:11.200
♪I trade the highest heaven and endless clouds♪

44:11.400 --> 44:14.200
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

44:14.280 --> 44:17.680
♪Pierced by countless arrows, pain and illness pile on♪

44:17.680 --> 44:21.000
♪Yet I remain silent♪

44:21.160 --> 44:25.000
♪Deep love and long yearning, a kiss falls into a dream♪

44:25.160 --> 44:28.360
♪In the distant night, bitterness blooms♪

44:28.600 --> 44:34.440
♪The grand chapter is rewritten, startling the whole world♪

44:35.000 --> 44:38.920
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

44:39.200 --> 44:41.960
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

44:42.160 --> 44:44.000
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

44:44.160 --> 44:48.360
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

44:48.600 --> 44:52.480
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

44:52.720 --> 44:55.760
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

44:55.960 --> 45:02.680
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

45:02.720 --> 45:06.680
♪If the seal can't be broken, then let it go♪

45:06.920 --> 45:09.680
♪Where the heart finds peace, there is home♪

45:09.800 --> 45:11.720
♪Side by side, we fly through seas of clouds♪

45:11.880 --> 45:16.160
♪Break through the waves; the heart's ocean knows no shore♪

45:16.360 --> 45:20.200
♪Always, at the very end of fate♪

45:20.440 --> 45:23.560
♪Comes that one moment of defiance♪

45:23.600 --> 45:29.600
♪In the human world or above, like flowing water and falling petals♪

45:30.000 --> 45:34.360
♪Let this fleeting life be whatever it may♪
